snippet.title: Kanye West Will ‘Do Anything’ To Get Kim Kardashian Back: He’s Very Upset She’s Dating Pete Davidson
snippet.description:
Kanye West Will ‘Do Anything’ To Get Kim Kardashian Back: He’s ‘Very Upset’ She’sDating Pete Davidson

#kanyewest #kimkardashian #petedavidson

Ye, commonly known by his former name Kanye West, is an American rapper, record producer, and fashion designer. 

Kimberly Noel Kardashian West is an American media personality, socialite, model, and businesswoman. Kardashian first gained media attention as a friend and stylist of Paris Hilton but received wider notice after a 2002 sex tape, Kim Kardashian, Superstar, with her then-boyfriend Ray J was released in 2007.

Peter Michael Davidson is an American comedian, actor, film producer, and screenwriter. He has been a cast member on the NBC late-night sketch comedy Saturday Night Live since 2014. Davidson has also appeared on the MTV shows Guy Code, Wild 'n Out, and Failosophy.
